snippet.title: Luna (In Development) Preview
snippet.description:
My first project with Unity, in development for about a year now. I just finished the final level and scene of the game. To celebrate, I made this silly video. Give it two to six months more of polish and we'll be done!

Music by Vinnie Byrne
Everything else by me, aka lushboy studios
